      { q:"Which ACE framework is used to collaboratively reset Bill's goals?", opts:["The ACE Mover Method and ACE ABC Approach","The FITT-only method","A prescriptive diet handout","Maximal intensity testing"], ans:0, exp:"The chapter applies the ACE Mover Method and ACE ABC Approach (Ask, Break down barriers, Collaborate)." }
    ]
